# Placeholder Icon Files

This theme references the following icon files that should be created:

- favicon-16x16.png
- favicon-32x32.png  
- apple-touch-icon.png (180x180)
- android-chrome-192x192.png
- android-chrome-512x512.png

## Recommended Tools for Icon Generation:

1. **Online Generators:**
   - https://realfavicongenerator.net/
   - https://favicon.io/

2. **Design Tools:**
   - Use the favicon.svg as a base design
   - Maintain Swiss design principles: clean lines, minimal colors
   - Use white background with black geometric elements
   - Add red accent in corner for brand recognition

3. **PWA Icon Requirements:**
   - All icons should be square
   - Follow PWA maskable icon guidelines for Android
   - Test on various devices and browsers

## Temporary Solution:
The favicon.svg will work as a fallback for modern browsers until PNG versions are created.